In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Michael A. CASALE. No. D-2715. Supreme Court of the United States June 17, 2013.

Michael A. Casale, of Fairfield, New Jersey, is suspended from the practice of *2847law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
